<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Mapleton Springs B&B</title>
    <meta name="description" content="" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header></Header>

    <main class="text-green1 py-5 bg-off-white">
      <h1 class="text-center text-2xl">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <ol class="list-disc px-7 py-5 space-y-5 text-xl">
        <li class="m-auto max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="font-bold">Do I get a refund if I have to cancel due to COVID lockdown?</h2>
          <p class="italic">Yes. Full refunds are provided.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="m-auto max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="font-bold">Can I bring a baby/child?</h2>
          <p class="italic">No. We are an adult only resort.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="m-auto max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="font-bold">Is breakfast included in the tariff?</h2>
          <p class="italic">No.  Breakfast is not provided at Mapleton Springs. There is a fridge, toaster, kettle and
            microwave in each room.  There are also a range of cafes in Mapleton (5 mins drive).</p>
        </li>
        <li class="m-auto max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="font-bold">What time is check-in and check out?</h2>
          <p class="italic">Check-in is 2pm and check out is 10am.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="m-auto max-w-xl">
          <h2 class="font-bold">Can I buy a gift voucher for a stay?</h2>
          <p class="italic">Yes.  For more details select <a class="underline" href="vouchers.html">VOUCHERS.</a></p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </main>

    <Footer></Footer>
  </body>
</html>
